Nitidotachinus excellens
: Campbell 1995: 45; 
Herman 2001
: 850; 
Smetana 2004
: 340; 

Schuelke
2005

: 170.

Body (Fig. 1
G-H
) medium in size, 4.5-5.9 mm (total length); 3.1-3.4 mm (length of forebody). Color dark brown with shine; the first and second segments of antennae, mouthparts, sides and posterior margin of pronotum, posterior margins of elytra, and legs yellowish red.
